From ea25974413e6000fd81459f7e672cc7ac45f9c43 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Frogging-Family
From: damachine <damachin3@proton.me>
Date: Mon, 27 Apr 2026 21:14:49 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] fixes, dkms-clang

Misc kernel additions (6.18+):
- x86/tlb: move sync_core_before_usermode() to tlbflush.h
- bluetooth: btusb quirk addition
- sched: topology cleanup, remove unused FEAT_NI flags, core.c simplification
- scripts: clang/warn Makefile cleanup
- ksysfs: add uevent_seqnum sysfs knob

Signed-off-by: damachine <damachin3@proton.me>

